text: Bernhard Dahl (23 November 1898 - 14 February 1963) was a Norwegian diver. He competed in the men's plain high diving event at the 1920 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1898 births Category:1963 deaths Category:Norwegian male divers Category:Olympic divers of Norway Category:Divers at the 1920 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bergen
